flowchart TD
    Start([DOM Content Loaded]) --> InitGame[initializeGame]
    InitGame --> SetVars[Set Variables: width=28, score=0]
    SetVars --> CreateLayout[Define Layout Array<br/>0=pac-dot, 1=wall, 2=ghost-lair,<br/>3=power-pellet, 4=empty]
    CreateLayout --> CreateBoard[createBoard]
    CreateBoard --> Loop1{For each cell<br/>in layout}
    Loop1 --> CreateSquare[Create div element]
    CreateSquare --> AddClass[addClassToSquare:<br/>Add CSS class based on cell type]
    AddClass --> Loop1
    Loop1 --> |Done|CreatePacman[createPacman at position 490]
    CreatePacman --> AddKeyListener[Add keyup event listener]
    AddKeyListener --> InitGhosts[initializeGhosts:<br/>Create 4 ghosts with positions]
    InitGhosts --> Loop2{For each ghost}
    Loop2 --> MoveGhost[moveGhost: Start interval timer]
    MoveGhost --> Loop2
    Loop2 --> |Done|Idle[Game Running - Wait for Events]
    
    Idle --> |Key Press|MovePacman[movePacman]
    MovePacman --> RemoveOld[Remove pac-man class from current position]
    RemoveOld --> KeyCheck{Which Arrow Key?}
    KeyCheck --> |Left|MoveLeftFunc[moveLeft]
    KeyCheck --> |Up|MoveUpFunc[moveUp]
    KeyCheck --> |Right|MoveRightFunc[moveRight]
    KeyCheck --> |Down|MoveDownFunc[moveDown]
    
    MoveLeftFunc --> CheckBlocked1{Not at edge &<br/>not blocked?}
    MoveUpFunc --> CheckBlocked2{Not at edge &<br/>not blocked?}
    MoveRightFunc --> CheckBlocked3{Not at edge &<br/>not blocked?}
    MoveDownFunc --> CheckBlocked4{Not at edge &<br/>not blocked?}
    
    CheckBlocked1 --> |Yes|UpdatePos1[Update position -1]
    CheckBlocked1 --> |No|KeepPos1[Keep position]
    CheckBlocked2 --> |Yes|UpdatePos2[Update position -width]
    CheckBlocked2 --> |No|KeepPos2[Keep position]
    CheckBlocked3 --> |Yes|UpdatePos3[Update position +1]
    CheckBlocked3 --> |No|KeepPos3[Keep position]
    CheckBlocked4 --> |Yes|UpdatePos4[Update position +width]
    CheckBlocked4 --> |No|KeepPos4[Keep position]
    
    UpdatePos1 --> AddNew[Add pac-man class to new position]
    KeepPos1 --> AddNew
    UpdatePos2 --> AddNew
    KeepPos2 --> AddNew
    UpdatePos3 --> AddNew
    KeepPos3 --> AddNew
    UpdatePos4 --> AddNew
    KeepPos4 --> AddNew
    
    AddNew --> HandleDot[handlePacDotEaten]
    HandleDot --> DotCheck{Has pac-dot class?}
    DotCheck --> |Yes|AddScore1[score++, update display,<br/>remove pac-dot]
    DotCheck --> |No|HandlePower
    AddScore1 --> HandlePower[handlePowerPelletEaten]
    
    HandlePower --> PowerCheck{Has power-pellet class?}
    PowerCheck --> |Yes|AddScore2[score+=10, update display]
    PowerCheck --> |No|CheckGameOver
    AddScore2 --> ScareGhosts[scareGhosts: Set all ghosts.isScared=true]
    ScareGhosts --> SetTimer[setTimeout to unScareGhosts after 10s]
    SetTimer --> RemovePower[Remove power-pellet class]
    RemovePower --> CheckGameOver
    
    CheckGameOver[checkForGameOver] --> GOCheck{Has ghost class &<br/>NOT scared-ghost?}
    GOCheck --> |Yes|GameOver[Stop all ghosts, remove listener,<br/>alert Game Over]
    GOCheck --> |No|CheckWin
    GameOver --> End([Game Ended])
    
    CheckWin[checkForWin] --> WinCheck{score >= 274?}
    WinCheck --> |Yes|Win[Stop all ghosts, remove listener,<br/>alert You have WON!]
    WinCheck --> |No|BackIdle
    Win --> End
    BackIdle[Return to Idle] --> Idle
    
    Idle --> |Ghost Timer|GhostMove[Ghost Movement Interval]
    GhostMove --> CanMove{canMoveToSquare?}
    CanMove --> |Yes|MoveGhostSquare[moveGhostToNewSquare:<br/>Remove from old, add to new]
    CanMove --> |No|NewDirection[Pick random direction]
    NewDirection --> CheckCollision
    MoveGhostSquare --> CheckCollision[checkGhostCollision]
    CheckCollision --> IsScared{ghost.isScared &<br/>has pacman class?}
    IsScared --> |Yes|EatGhost[Reset ghost position,<br/>score+=100]
    IsScared --> |No|ContinueGhost
    EatGhost --> ContinueGhost[Continue ghost interval]
    ContinueGhost --> Idle